{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>總是為了影片檔案太大而煩惱嗎？Squeeze – Video Compressor 這款強大的影片壓縮工具，能幫助您將影片大小最高縮減 90%，畫質卻幾乎無損，是釋放手機儲存空間、方便分享至 WhatsApp、上傳社群媒體或透過 Email 傳送影片的絕佳幫手，現在限時免費提供終生版，是您不容錯過的機會。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-83.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>手機空間瞬間解放</h2>\n    <p>Squeeze – Video Compressor 透過先進的 H.264 與 H.265 (HEVC) 編碼技術，結合 Apple VideoToolbox 硬體加速，能在裝置本地端進行高效能影片壓縮，保護您的隱私與安全，即使離線也能順暢使用，支援匯入 Photos 或 Files 中的各種影片格式，並能依照 WhatsApp、Instagram、TikTok 等平台最佳化，一鍵套用專屬格式，讓影片分享與儲存變得前所未有的輕鬆簡便。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1125x2436bb.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1125x2436bb-1.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1125x2436bb-2.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1125x2436bb-3.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1125x2436bb-4.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1125x2436bb-5.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <h2>限時免費領取終生版</h2>\n    <p>Squeeze – Video Compressor 終生版內購限時免費中，用戶完成初始化後看到收費牆，Lifetime 價格顯示為$0 即可免費收下。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/IMG_2953-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 2953\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/IMG_2954-473x1024.webp\" alt=\"IMG 2954\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Squeeze – Video Compressor</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Photo &amp; Video</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T10:12:39.812776+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":536,"images":9,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}